Results.ReviewText: I bought Nescafe Gold Decaffeinated when the supermarket had none of my usual choice on the shelves.  Per cup,  the taste of gold is as good as a trip to Brazil to taste  a freshly brewed cup. Nescafe Gold is now my first choice when selecting coffee.
Results.Title: First Choice

Results.ReviewText: I started drinking decaf coffee a few years ago in the evenings but never managed to find one that tasted as nice as my morning coffee. Having found Nescafé good blend decaf I can finally enjoy evening coffees as much as those I have in the morning!
Results.Title: As good if not better than the original!

Results.ReviewText: MY daughter bought Nescafe Gold Blend home and asked me to try it.  Been a tea man all my life 79 years . The Taste made me change my way  I find my self going          for coffee with the name Nescafe.        sorry not good enough to put a photo in
Results.Title: THE TASTE THAT STAY WITH YOU

Results.UserLocation: Tyn y Groes, Conwy, North Wales
Results.ReviewText: When i was advised to give up caffeine I was so worried my coffee hit would never be the same again. How wrong could I be! I still get the great taste of a 'real' coffee with Nescafe  Gold Blend Decaff, so thank you for satisfying my taste buds!
Results.Title: Decaff with the grest taste of nescafe gold!

Results.ReviewText: I purchase this coffee by mistake- it was meant to be an own brand product, really happy I did !! Was the best mistake purchase ever!! Real intense flavour and aromatic ... will not buy it as a mistake next time, I will add it to my regular list
Results.Title: Nescafé gold blend decaf

Results.ReviewText: I have tried numerous Decaff coffee,s and this is the one and only coffee i can honestly say is worth buying, the taste is wonderfully rich and smooth, with a distinct taste way above any competitiors, Just try it you wont drink any other....
Results.Title: Simply the Best!

Results.ReviewText: I always buy decaff coffee and up until now I've always bought a competitor's one but after tasting Nescafe Gold Blend Decaff there is no comparison - SO tasty, smooth and refreshing.  My mouth is watering now so I'd better go and make a cup!
Results.Title: Sooo yummy

Results.ReviewText: This coffee has a full bodied, well rounded flavour of a fully caffeinated coffee but it is a decaff. I love the fact that I can drink this coffee without worrying about my caffeine intake and I still get a really great tasting cup of coffee.
Results.Title: Excellent taste, you wouldn't know it was decaff

Results.ReviewText: I bought decaff by mistake and found it rich in flavor and very smooth. I served it to my friends and they were surprised it was decaff and had a second cup. price wise you have us sold. I intend to try other Nescafe varieties on my friends.
Results.Title: Nescafe gold

Results.ReviewText: I'm always being accused of having expensive tastes so this suits me perfectly for it tastes expensive. Delicious, full flavoured and aromatic brew, you wouldn't believe it was either instant or decaff. A real treat at an affordable price.
Results.Title: Expensive Tastes!

Results.ReviewText: I tried this instead of my usual Nescafe decaf coffee which I've had for many, many years and I'm converted.  The smooth mellow taste is lovely and instead of leaving a quarter of a mug as usual which annoys my husband, I drink a full mug!
Results.Title: Fab smooth taste

Results.ReviewText: I love all Nescafé products! This product has a great taste, but if I'm honest it's not as good as Nescafé decaf original! Nescafé gold blend doesn't dissolve completely in the bottom of the cup, so it's back to the original for me! Sorry!
Results.Title: Loving the gold!

Results.ReviewText: I always buy this product so I normally go straight to it. But since the label change it took longer to find. I was disappointed to find that wasn't the only change. The taste is the same but it leaves a sediment at the bottom of the cup!
Results.Title: Decaffeinated new nescafe

Results.ReviewText:
I bought this a couple of days and I was surprised to see it in Decaf i these new brands as I can only drink Decaf.
It's a smooth taste with a rich flavour even my said it was like drinking fresh coffe and they didn't know it was Decaf.
Results.Title: Great Taste

Results.ReviewText: I was worried when finding I have to have decaffeinated coffee later on in  the day now, but needn't have.  This Nescafe Gold is just as flavorsome as the regular and I find myself checking that it is the correct jar!  Well done Nestle!!
Results.Title: Decaff . . are you sure!!

Results.ReviewText: I decided to move to decaf as any other caffeneited coffee never gave me a buzz or made me crave caffeine, so I thought 'I wonder what decaf would be like'.  I have tried numerous coffee brands, and this is my joint first.  Really tasty
Results.Title: Lovely - All of the flavour, none ofthe caffeine

Results.ReviewText: Have stopped to decaffeinated tea and coffee. Have tried several different decaffei ated coffees and this is probably one of tge better ones. Have always used Gold Blend when I want an instant coffee . Will probably stick with this one.
Results.Title: One of the better decaffeinated coffees

Results.ReviewText: I am a coffee addict, but constantly nagged by my husband because he thinks I shouldn't  drink it at night. Most decaff tastes horrible, but nescafe is lovely. Now both husband and wife are happy and he even drinks some occasionally.
Results.Title: Coffee at night

Results.ReviewText: I have always chosen caffeinated coffee before but decided to try decaff for health reasons.  Well, I am happy to say that it is hard to taste any difference between the two so from here on in, it is Nescafe Gold Blend Decaff for me.
Results.Title: Decaff Gold Blend

Results.ReviewText: i bought this 3 weeks ago while on promotion and boy is it great- husband didnt even know it was decoff and he said he really loves it- great taste nescafe you came up with the real gold in this coffee- scrumptious flavour thank you
Results.Title: best tasting coffee- love this coffee

Results.ReviewText: Best decaff I have tried for a while, I take mine white with a grain of sugar, flavour is lovely and you wouldnt know it was decaff. None of the bitterness you get with some brands. Excellent value will definitely be buying again.
Results.Title: Super smooth decaff with no loss of flavour

Results.ReviewText: I have avoided coffee for years as it seemed to disagree with me, but then had Nescafe Gold Decaf at a friend's house recently... So pleased I did! Rich, flavoursome and didn't disagree with me. Looks like I can have coffee again!
Results.Title: Quite simply, delicious!

Results.ReviewText: bought this as my regular brand was out of stock and was pleasantly suprised at the taste. Great taste, lovely full bodied coffee and a wonderful aroma. What more caould you ask for? will deffinetly be buying this in the future :)
Results.Title: Very Moreish.........

Results.ReviewText: I've always been a Nescafe coffee drinker & it continues to maintain if not improve in its richness & smoothness qualities. I've switched to Decaf this year & the enjoyment has not deminished. In fact I can't tell the difference.
Results.Title: Smooth & delicious

Results.ReviewText: I bought this because my usual coffee coffee was sold out and Im very glad i did! The aroma and taste is perfect and is exactly what i'm looking for in a coffee break. A big fat YES I will defiantly be buying this from now on :)
Results.Title: Great Aroma

Results.ReviewText: I bought this initially for my bedtime drink about six weeks ago - I am now on my third jar - and am really impressed that there is virtually no difference in taste to the Gold Blend that I enjoy through the day.   Well done!!!
Results.Title: Excellant taste

Results.ReviewText:
Nescafé Gold Blend is the only decaf I will buy.  Rich smooth flavour provides a great coffee hut without the caffeine which I can’t tolerate.
Have noticed that the new product leaves a sludgy residue at the bottom of the cup.
Results.Title: Great taste

Results.ReviewText: I buy this for my husband but only when the coffee is on offer, as it is quite pricey and I often buy own supermarket products, unless Nescafe are beating their price!  My husband loves it and says the taste quality is superb.
Results.Title: Superb coffee

Results.ReviewText: We have enjoyed drinking Gold Blend Decaff (with the blue lid) for many years.  We have tried other brands and always come back to it.  This new formulation tastes flat and bitter and we would like our old blend back, please!
Results.Title: A backward step!

Results.ReviewText: i only buy nescafe ,my partner prefers de caff ,and she demands the best ,hence i only buy nescafe gold.i also like this ,but always keep nescafe original in cupboard for myself and visitors ,so i have the best of both worlds
Results.Title: only coffee i buy ,excellent quality
